2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a preprocessing method to improve the robustness of exemplar-based methods, which are often based on machine learning techniques.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the synthesis of face sketches, which can be considered an application of AI.
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with the generation of visual content (face sketches).
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the synthesis of multimedia content (face sketches) using exemplar-based methods.
